==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: manganese bronze
<hw>manganese bronze</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A brass alloy having from 1
to 4 percent of manganese added to harden it; made by adding manganese
to the copper and zinc used in brass.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> high-strength brass.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Manganese steel</ent>⟦br⟧
